|-----------|-------|--------|-----------|
| Constants | 4 (`"quote"`, `0`, `0`, `1.5`) | ×1 | 4 |
| Bindings | 7 (`scenario`, `results`, `step`, `basePremium`, `item`, `itemBase`, `premium`) | ×1 | 7 |
| Invocations | 2 (`Math.floor`, `results.push`) | ×2 | 4 |
| Conditionals | 4 (`if`, `?? []`, `?? 0`, `?:`) | ×4 | 16 |
